data.title: Seth Green
data.meta_description: Seth Benjamin Green (born Seth Benjamin Gesshel-Green; February 8, 1974) is an American actor. He served as an executive producer for the Stoopid Buddy Stoodios couch gags. He also voiced Chris Griffin in Family Guy's season 13 premiere "The Simpsons Guy", a The Simpsons/Family Guy crossover, the Nerd in the "Robot Chicken couch gag 2", and Mav Redfield in the season 33 episode "Meat Is Murder".

Seth Benjamin Green (born Seth Benjamin Gesshel-Green; February 8, 1974) is an American actor. He served as an executive producer for the Stoopid Buddy Stoodios couch gags. He also voiced Chris Griffin in Family Guy's season 13 premiere "The Simpsons Guy", a The Simpsons/Family Guy crossover, the Nerd in the "Robot Chicken couch gag 2", and Mav Redfield in the season 33 episode "Meat Is Murder".
